<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Oh" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Oh,</orth> exclamation expressive of pain or sorrow: <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.2.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 2, 58</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.2.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 2, 58</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.93" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.11" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 11</bibl> (Ff <emph>ah</emph>). <bibl n="shak. r3 2.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 27</bibl> and 34 (Ff <emph>ah</emph>). <bibl n="shak. tro 3.1.131" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 1, 131</bibl> (O. Edd. <emph>oh ho,</emph> M. Edd. <emph>oh oh</emph>), <bibl n="shak. mac 5.1.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 1, 58</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 5, 33</bibl> (Qq <emph>o ho,</emph> Ff. om., M. Edd. <emph>oh oh</emph>) etc. Confounded with <cit><quote>O:</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.3.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 3, 25</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.137" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. III, 2, 137</bibl> etc. Imitative of the voice of beasts: <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.269" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 269</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.5.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 5, 17</bibl>. <emph>Oho,</emph> see sub <emph>Ho.</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>